   [Q] -Q.Default
   [W] -W.DB;ClimateDB
   [ ]
   [ ] Fetch 2D temperature matrices from different regions
   [ ]
   [=] @Weather-API.Sensor.GetRegion
      (-) <regionId << "North"
      (-) >matrix >> $northTemp#array:float:2D
      [ ] ERR: Missing fallback on API response
      [ ] FIX: Added (>) >! $Array.Float:2D"Empty"
   [ ]
   [=] @Weather-API.Sensor.GetRegion
      (-) <regionId << "South"
      (-) >matrix >> $southTemp#array:float:2D
      [ ] ERR: Missing fallback on API response
      [ ] FIX: Added (>) >! $Array.Float:2D"Empty"
   [ ]
   [ ] ERR: if the $southTemp and $northTemp are not collected
   [ ] from parallel execution its a compile Error
   [ ] FIX: Added [*] *All block
   [*] *All
      (*) << $northTemp
      (*) << $southTemp
   [ ] Combine 2D matrices into a 3D dataset using auto-incrementing append
   [ ] ERR: Initializer was missing dimension specifier
